quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  49,14,"Abarabu bo mu cyaro (batuye mu butayu) baravuze bati “Twaremeye!” Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ntimuremera, ahubwo nimuvuge muti twabaye Abayisilamu”, kuko ukwemera kutarinjira mu mitima yanyu. Ariko nimwumvira Allah n’Intumwa ye, nta cyo azagabanya mu bikorwa byanyu. Mu by’ukuri Allah ni Ubabarira bihebuje, Nyirimbabazi"
  49,15,"Mu by’ukuri abemeramana nyabo ni abemeye Allah n’Intumwa ye, hanyuma ntibashidikanye (ku byo bemeye), bakanaharanira inzira ya Allah bakoresheje imitungo yabo n’ubuzima bwabo. Abo ni bo banyakuri"
  49,16,Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ese murigisha Allah iby’idini ryanyu mu gihe Allah azi ibiri mu birere n’ibiri mu isi? Kandi Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje wa buri kintu.”
  49,17,Barakuratira ko babaye Abayisilamu (nk’aho ari wowe bifitiye akamaro)? Vuga uti “Mwindatatira ubuyisilamu bwanyu (mwibwira ko ari njye bufitiye akamaro). Ahubwo Allah ni We wabagiriye ubuntu abayobora mu kwemera niba koko muri abanyakuri.”
  49,18,Mu by’ukuri Allah azi ibitagaragara byo mu birere no mu isi. Kandi Allah ni Ubona bihebuje ibyo mukora
  50,1,Qaaf. Ndahiye iyi Qur’an yuje ikuzo
  50,2,Ahubwo batangajwe n’uko umuburizi yaje aturutse muri bo. Bityo abahakanyi baravuga bati “Iki ni ikintu gitangaje.”
  50,3,Ese nidupfa tugahinduka igitaka (tuzazurwa)? Uko kugaruka kuri kure (ntikwabaho)
  50,4,Rwose tuzi neza icyo ubutaka bugenda bugabanyaho (ku mibiri yabo igihe bari mu mva). Kandi dufite igitabo kirinzwe (kibitse buri kintu)
  50,5,"Nyamara bahinyuye ukuri ubwo kwabageragaho; bityo, barahuzagurika (ntibashobora gutandukanya ukuri n’ikinyoma)"
  50,6,"Ese ntibitegereza ikirere kiri hejuru yabo uko twacyubatse maze tukanagitaka, kikaba nta n’imyenge gifite"
  50,7,"N’isi twarayishashe maze tuyishimangiza imisozi, nuko tuyimezaho buri bwoko bw’ibimera bushimishije"
  50,8,(Ibi twabikoze kugira ngo bibe) isomo n’urwibutso kuri buri mugaragu (wa Allah) wicuza
  50,9,"Twanamanuye amazi yuje imigisha (imvura) aturutse mu kirere, maze tuyameresha imirima n’impeke zisarurwa"
  50,10,N’imitende miremire ifite amaseri ahekeranye neza
  50,11,Kugira ngo bibe amafunguro ku bagaragu banjye. Tunayahesha ubuzima ubutaka bwapfuye. Uko ni ko izuka ry’abapfuye rizagenda
  50,12,"Mbere yabo (abahakanyi b’i Maka), abantu ba Nuhu n’abari baturiye iriba rya Rasi ndetse n’abantu bo mu bwoko bwa Thamudu bahinyuye intumwa zabo"
  50,13,N’aba Adi na Farawo ndetse n’abavandimwe ba Lutwi (Loti)
  50,14,"N’abantu ba Ayikat (b’i Madiyani), n’abantu ba Tubba’i (abami bo mu gihugu cya Yemeni) bose bahinyuye intumwa zabo, maze mbasohorezaho isezerano ryanjye (ryo kubahana)"
  50,15,Ese twaba twarananijwe n’ukurema kwa mbere (ku buryo ukurema kwa kabiri kwatunanira)? Ahubwo bari mu gushidikanya ku kurema gushya (izuka)
  50,16,Mu by’ukuri twaremye umuntu kandi tuzi ibyo umutima we umwoshya. Kandi tumuri bugufi kurusha umutsi w’ubuzima (wo mu ijosi; ujyana amaraso mu bwonko)
  50,17,"(Zirikana) ko abakira babiri (abamalayika bashinzwe gukurikirana umuntu), bakira (ibyo avuga n’ibyo akora); umwe yicaye iburyo undi ibumoso"
  50,18,(Umuntu) nta jambo na rimwe yavuga ngo habure umugenzuzi umuri hafi (uryandika)
  50,19,Kandi ibimenyetso bibimburira urupfu bigaragaza ukuri bizaza nta kabuza.. (Maze abwirwe ati) “Ibyo ni byo wajyaga wihunza”
  50,20,"Nuko impanda nivuzwa, uwo ni wo uzaba ari umunsi w’ibihano (umunsi w’izuka)"
  50,21,Buri muntu azaza ari kumwe n’(umumalayika) umushoreye ndetse n’(umumalayika) umushinja
  50,22,"(Umunyabyaha azabwirwa ati) “Rwose wari mu burangare (utita) kuri ibi, ariko twagukuyeho igikingirizo (cyakingirizaga umutima wawe), none uyu munsi amaso yawe yatyaye (arabona byose).”"
  50,23,Umusangirangendo we (malayika umushinzwe) azavuga ati “Iki (ni cyo gitabo cy’ibikorwa bye) gitunganyije mfite.”
  50,24,(Allah azabwira abo bamalayika bombi ati) “Nimujugunye mu muriro wa Jahanamu buri muhakanyi wigometse”
  50,25,"Ubangamira ibyiza, urengera kandi ushidikanya"
  50,26,Wa wundi wabangikanyije Allah n’indi mana. Nimumujugunye mu bihano bikaze